Attribution and scope
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

HISS Finance is compilation and verification software. It prepares, simulates,
scores, and records financial primitives. It does not take custody of assets,
does not hold user keys, does not place brokerage orders, and does not guarantee
any financial outcome.

HISS Finance is not affiliated with, endorsed by, or sponsored by Robinhood
Markets, Inc., Bankr, Doppler, Chainlink Labs, Uniswap Labs, or any other third
